{
  "name": "RPlog_Ground_Battle_on_Sullust",
  "title": "The Ground Battle on Sullust",
  "summary": "The Empire launches its long-awaited ground assault on the volcanic world of Sullust, dropping waves of stormtroopers under the veteran commander TK-2501 onto the spaceport beachhead while Scimitar bombers and TIE Interceptors soften the defenses. The dug-in Sullustan and New Republic forces, led by a fierce Sullustan Captain, the Horansi Major Snarl, the part-Cathari Major Shau'ri, General Unnh, and the freshly field-promoted Cadet Krieger, funnel the invaders into a deadly U-shaped killzone of rigged platforms, snipers, and grenade barrages. The stormtroopers blast their way into the sublevels to destroy the power generators and knock out the starport's defense guns, while above, Admiral Danik Kreldin watches from the HIMS Selene over wine and opera, conversing with the ex-marshal Valtoor about glory, casualties, and his resolve to take the planet 'all the way.' Over two brutal days the fighting seesaws; the Sullustans nearly retake the starport with a desperate counterattack, deploying the Sand Cats under Sergeant Frul to flood the bay with superheated geothermal water, but Kreldin betrays his own troops with a devastating orbital turbolaser barrage. The day ends with dozens dead on both sides, surrendering Imperials abandoned by their commanders, and the New Republic still clinging to the planet's freedom.",
